title: Finn | Adventure Time Wiki | Fandom
snippet: Finn Mertens (also known as Finn the Human) is the main protagonist in Adventure Time. He also appeared in the spin-off series Adventure Time: Distant Lands and returned in the spin-off series Adventure Time: Fionna & Cake. He was voiced by Jeremy Shada in most appearances.

title: Finn the Human - Wikipedia
snippet: Finn Mertens, better known as Finn the Human, is a character and one of the two protagonists, alongside Jake the Dog, of the American animated television series Adventure Time and its franchise created by Pendleton Ward.

title: Finn the Human - Adventure Time Wiki
snippet: Finn the Human 'or and formerly known as Pen' in the Animated Short is the main protagonist of the series Adventure Time. As shown in "Memories of Boom Boom Mountain," Finn appears to have been abandoned in the woods during infancy.
